-- Butt to Again Lead Axis Board as Charman Ousted as Chairman
-- B y   S t e v e n   N o r t o n
-- 2012-06-25T13:07:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-25/butt-to-again-lead-axis-board-as-charman-ousted-as-chairman.html
Axis Capital Holdings Ltd., the
Bermuda-based reinsurer, named Michael Butt to again lead the
board of directors after Chairman John Charman was ousted
following a dispute over his role.  Charman will remain on the board of directors, the company
said today in a statement distributed by  Business Wire .  To contact the reporter on this story:
